{% endfor %}

## 🎓 Recommendation

{% if data.recommendation %}
{{ emoji.info }} **Recommended Option**: {{ data.recommendation.option }}

{% if data.recommendation.reasoning %}
**Reasoning**:
{{ data.recommendation.reasoning }}
{% endif %}

{% if data.recommendation.confidence %}
**Confidence**: {{ health_score(data.recommendation.confidence, 'Recommendation Confidence') }}
{% endif %}
{% endif %}

## 👥 Stakeholder Impact

{% if data.stakeholder_impact %}
{% for stakeholder, impact in data.stakeholder_impact.items() %}
- **{{ stakeholder }}**: {{ impact.description }} ({{ status_indicator(impact.sentiment) }} {{ impact.sentiment }})
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

## ⚠️ Risks & Mitigation

